            <div type="transcript" id="P96-60">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>When roses cease to bloom, dear,</l>
                    <l>And violets are done,</l>
                    <l>When bumble-bees in solemn flight</l>
                    <l>Have passed beyond the sun,</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>The hand that paused to gather</l>
                    <l>Upon this summer's day</l>
                    <l>Will idle lie, in Auburn, </l>
                    <l>Then take my flower, pray!</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
